### System Architecture: Stereo Vision Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    %% Styling for GitHub Light/Dark Compatibility
    classDef input fill:#2b303b,stroke:#4f5b66,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef process fill:#4f5b66,stroke:#65737e,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef intermediate fill:#a7adba,stroke:#c0c5ce,stroke-width:2px,color:#000;
    classDef analytics fill:#343d46,stroke:#4f5b66,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef output fill:#bf616a,stroke:#d08770,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;

    subgraph Ingestion["1. Sensor Ingestion & Alignment"]
        k1[Left Camera Feed]:::input
        k2[Right Camera Feed]:::input
        Sync{"Frame Synchronization & Timestamping"}:::process
        Calib[("Calibration Matrices (Intrinsics/Extrinsics)")]:::input
        Rect["Image Rectification (Epipolar Alignment)"]:::process
        
        k1 & k2 --> Sync
        Sync --> Rect
        Calib -.-> Rect
    end

    subgraph StereoProc["2. Stereo Correspondence & Depth"]
        PreProc["Image Preprocessing (Denoising / Contrast)"]:::process
        Matching["Stereo Matching (SGM / Deep Learning)"]:::process
        RawDisp["Raw Disparity Map"]:::intermediate
        Filter["Disparity Post-Filtering (WLS / Hole Filling)"]:::process
        DepthCalc["Depth Map & 3D Point Cloud Generation"]:::intermediate
        
        Rect --> PreProc
        PreProc --> Matching
        Matching --> RawDisp
        RawDisp --> Filter
        Filter --> DepthCalc
    end

    subgraph Perception["3. Spatial Perception & Analytics"]
        ObjDet["Object Detection (YOLO / 2D-3D CNN)"]:::process
        Fusion["Spatial Data Fusion (Bounding Box + Depth)"]:::process
        Tracking["Temporal Tracking (Kalman Filter / SORT)"]:::process
        Hazards["Distance & Hazard Assessment (TTC Calculation)"]:::analytics
        
        Rect --> ObjDet
        ObjDet --> Fusion
        DepthCalc --> Fusion
        Fusion --> Tracking
        Tracking --> Hazards
    end

    subgraph OutLayer["4. Output Layer"]
        HUD["Visualization Engine / HUD"]:::output
        Control["Control / Actuation Signals (Optional)"]:::output
        
        Hazards --> HUD
        Hazards --> Control
    end